    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried everything. doctors, meds, therapy... nothing touches it. it's just this permanent, heavy weight. sometimes i look at the concept of \"non-existence\" and it doesn't even feel scary anymore. it just feels like the only thing that would actually be peaceful. like, wouldn't it be a mercy to just finally have some stillness?",
