      "content": "it's just hard because everyone keeps talking about \"fighting\" or \"managing,\" but it feels like they don't get it. it's not something to fight, it's just... it's a broken system. when you're in this much agony every single day, isn't it just a logical conclusion to want it to stop? to just have the quiet? it feels more like kindness than anything else.",
